description: The Markit iBoxx EUR Eurozone (DE ES FR IT NL) 25+ Index aims to reflect the performance of the following market: EUR-denominated bonds issued by governments of the Eurozone Bonds with maturities over 25 years Investment grade bonds only Minimum amount outstanding of EUR 1 billion per bond Additional information on the Index and the general methodology behind the Markit iBoxx indices can be found on Markit iBoxx website ( https://www.markit.com ).
name: Xtrackers II Eurozone Government Bond 25+ UCITS ETF 1C
